Secure post/comment/like ownership rules.
PostService still accepts usernames from requests for create/update/like/comment. Replace that with authenticated user from SecurityContextHolder.
Also enforce:
only owner can edit/delete post
only owner or admin can delete comment
banned users cannot create content

Add admin-only moderation APIs.
Current admin post handling is weak because /api/posts/admin just returns getFeed() and delete uses normal delete logic.
Add explicit admin service methods protected by role checks.

Add missing repositories and DTOs for reports and notifications.

Add tests.
Minimum useful tests:
auth register/login
subscribe/unsubscribe
cannot subscribe to self
